{"tid":2013310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汶川地震12周年  習近平到山西見佛","createTime":"2020-05-12T08:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T15:54:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a41e6431bef6d4f149b049f5fa805cd977dcd7e8","tid":2013310,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"據大陸官媒報導，5月11日傍晚，習近平來到山西大同市武州山南麓的雲岡石窟考察。他走進具有代表性的特色石窟仔細查看雕塑、壁畫，詳細詢問石窟開鑿歷史、藝術風格、文物保護等情況，並同在場的「遊客」交流、揮手致意。<br />\n<br />\n央視畫面顯示，習到訪之際，現場「適時」走出一群明顯是安排好的「群眾演員」和習一行人不期而遇，對習熱烈揮手致意。隨後，歡迎的人群令習滿臉歡喜。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img3.secretchina.com/pic/2020/5-12/p2688341a404532038-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg3.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2020%2F5-12%2Fp2688341a404532038-ss.jpg&h=d47ff364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：視頻截圖） <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/05/12/933004.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2F933004.html&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a30453eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/05/12/933004.html</a>"},{"pid":"78a07cf0f601f871ba7bf462de02384f67d5d14f","tid":2013310,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"滿臉歡喜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406a3b8759506339206ce98c629a53b3a1ff4e11","tid":2013310,"uid":346806,"like":10,"dislike"